Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}它在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:59.89,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}如果感到厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:04.56,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}那就  革旧&立新
